So we'll do print, and then inside of the print statement,

78

00:04:54,380  -->  00:04:59,060
we'll say F to define the opener of our F string,

79

00:04:59,060  -->  00:05:00,560
and then we'll write text,

80

00:05:00,560  -->  00:05:02,120
add in our variable inputs,

81

00:05:02,120  -->  00:05:03,760
defined with squiggly brackets,

82

00:05:03,760  -->  00:05:07,180
and then close the F string with a closing quotation mark,

83

00:05:07,180  -->  00:05:10,050
