84

00:05:10,050  -->  00:05:15,620
To write this, we'll say you are age years old,

85

00:05:15,620  -->  00:05:22,600
and we'll define another variable input as a temple literal with height meters tall.

86

00:05:22,600  -->  00:05:24,640
Now, when this print statement is executed,

87

00:05:24,640  -->  00:05:27,520
